---
title: Easy-Peasy Ravioli Gratin with Spinach, Thyme, and Parmesan Breadcrumbs
description: Just when we thought pasta night couldn’t get any better, our chefs doubled down on the spinach. The nutritious green can be found both inside the ravioli *and* as a fresh, leafy mix-in between the pasta shells. But this dish is more than just a veggie-lover’s delight: there’s also a thick and creamy sauce and toasted breadcrumb topping to keep things comfy, cozy, and utterly delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bb4d835ae08b502a021dce2-9f4400e3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/easy-peasy-ravioli-gratin-5bb4d835ae08b502a021dce2-423007d1.pdf
